                                             List<org.apache.http.Header> headers,

                                             List<org.apache.http.NameValuePair> params,

                                             com.google.gson.JsonElement content)
        The handling function of JsonRestHandler.

        This method has the same signature as JsonRestHandler.handleParsedContent(List, List, JsonElement) , and can be used in RestHandlerFactory.createJsonRestHandler(JsonRestHandlerFunction) to set its behavior.

        Parameters:
        headers - the HTTP headers of the received request
        params - the request parameters
        content - the JsonElement representing the content of the HTTP request
        Returns:
        the JsonElement containing the endpoint response, or null
        See Also:
        RestHandlerFactory.createJsonRestHandler(JsonRestHandlerFunction)
